    "description": "Are you a skilled Full Stack Developer looking for your next big career move? Aptech South Asia Partners in Bhopal offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Aptech South Asia Partners:\nAptech South Asia Partners is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Microservices\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in Node.js\n• Proficiency in Rust\n• Proficiency in Git\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Flexible working hours\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Bhopal, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Aptech South Asia Partners!",
